      "content": "Accepting the void is a valid choice, but it is also the only way to stop the exhausting, pointless struggle you feel right now. If the end result is nothingness, then the only thing that matters is how you choose to face that inevitable silence, not whether you can \"win\" against it. There is no need to fight the darkness if the goal is simply to let it be, and sometimes the greatest act of defiance is to sit in the cold and stare back at it without trying to fix it.",
